    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera 2 is a driver-focused specimen featuring the naturally aspirated 3.4L flat-six engine paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The M96 powerplant has been meticulously maintained, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The rear-wheel-drive chassis remains sharp and communicative, benefiting from an upgraded coilover suspension and refreshed control arm bushings for superior lateral stability. With a clean DME report and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, this Porsche offers the raw, analog feedback and high-revving performance that defines the era.",
